{"tid":2074276,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果： 中國唯一一宗武漢肺炎死者家屬索償案 武漢市中級人民法院：「不予立案」不能追責","createTime":"2020-06-22T03:40:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T11:32:38.000Z","uid":22556,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5e2cb24bf6a077f82bdb6e6d8741be0a759a4703","tid":2074276,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T03:40:11.000Z","msg":"中國暫時唯一一宗武漢肺炎死者家屬索償案，武漢市中級人民法院於上同三口頭通知原告人張海「不予立案」。<br />\n<br />\n除了法院拒絕受理，張海同時面對政權的不同打壓。張父的骨灰被政府自行下葬；他與其他家屬都被監控，張海更兩次被「邀請」到派出所，公安把微信群的聊天紀錄打印出來，逐條問他，他反問：「哪條法律規定不能建微信群，哪條法律規定我作為受害者不能追責。我作為一個受害者的家屬，難道我追責就是成為違法行為？真正造成疫情的一些人，同時這些幫兇，到目前為止，並沒有一個人受到懲罰。」<br />\n<br />\n【專訪】「父親是被害死」狀告政府第一人不予立案：人禍累死人 法律公平？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200622&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=61057193\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200622%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D61057193&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0FyWHaP8IcnP89ZPrefCyuoo%3D&h=079ca3f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200622%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D61057193&h=5b7a766e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200622&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=61057193</a>"},{"pid":"93b368c9d2e4cc45610bd2bbbb87e8a97308baf6","tid":2074276,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T04:33:58.000Z","msg":"好撚勇, 玩命<br />\n原告人直接去外國申庇護, make some noise好過啦"},{"pid":"fe4755e1f7e677b6765f538b526aac3a1be6a72d","tid":2074276,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T04:35:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c0ca1795ce5323ac0bb7ea27adcc6e01808025","tid":2074276,"uid":65638,"like":2,"dislike":3